graph TD
subgraph "Phase 1: Study Start-Up & Activation"
A[Protocol Finalized] --> B{Initial Regulatory Submissions};
B --> B1[FDA IND #15487 Active];
B --> B2[EMA CTA Submitted via CTIS];
B1 & B2 --> C[Investigator's Brochure Finalized];
C --> D{Site Selection & Feasibility (25 Sites)};
D --> E[IRB/EC Submission & Approval];
E --> F((Site Initiation Visit & Activation));
F --> G[Initial ICF Version Verified];
end
subgraph "Phase 2: Enrollment & Study Conduct"
G --> H[First Patient In (FPI): Q1 2025];
H --> I(Patient Screening & Consent);
I -- "Consent Valid" --> J[Randomization (Arm A/B)];
I -- "Screen Fail / Withdrawal" --> SF((Screen Failure));
J --> K[Treatment & Data Collection in Medidata Rave];
K --> L{Ongoing Monitoring & SDV};
L --> M[TMF Quality Control Checks];
M --> N{AE/SAE Detection};
N -- "SAE Identified" --> O{SAE Report to Sponsor < 24h};
O --> P[Regulatory & IRB/EC Reporting];
N -- "AE (Non-Serious)" --> K;
K --> Q[50% Enrollment Milestone: Q4 2025];
Q --> R{DMC Interim Analysis};
R -- "Continue Trial per DMC" --> K;
K --> S[Last Patient In (LPI): Q1 2026];
S --> T[Treatment & Follow-Up Complete];
end
subgraph "Phase 3: Study Close-Out & Reporting"
T --> U[Last Patient, Last Visit (LPLV)];
U --> V[Site Close-Out Visits];
V --> W[Final Data Cleaning & Query Resolution];
W --> X[Final Audit Trail Review];
X --> Y{Database Lock: Q3 2026};
Y --> Z[Final Statistical Analysis];
Z --> AA[Clinical Study Report (CSR) Finalized: Q3 2026];
end
3.0 Global Regulatory & Ethics Pathway
This section outlines the critical submission and approval pathways for a multi-regional trial,
emphasizing tracking and maintenance requirements.

